textView.string: Implementation of a special wheelchair for people with disabilities using Smart Technologies

Our aim is to make prototype or mini version of special chair that will use Voice recognition to work.So that people with disabilities could control and interact with their chairs by simply using their voices.
Akkassin Assel Akhanova Bagdina Bolekbayeva Anel Yussupova Araylim
